{"tid":2179181,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"出黎社會既你地仲有冇保留「舊中學同學」群組? ?","createTime":"2020-08-29T02:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T06:45:52.000Z","uid":188406,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c6cfd6c435ff636e5ecd044e00ade1eab0b8bd6b","tid":2179181,"uid":188406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:35:33.000Z","msg":"whatsapp，Facebook既舊同學仔群組雖然畢業後幾年平時都冇乜人講野出聲，早幾年我精神失常手痕退出群組，但唔知點解有d後悔，好L想入番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時諗番起d中學濕9回憶就好想搵下佢地呃下水吹...雖然同個別幾個都仲有偶約出黎一齊食飯，call G，但最後發現都係要成班人男男女女約哂出黎先會開心d。<br />\n<br />\n唔知出黎社會後既大家點睇d舊同學仔群組??<br />\n<br />\n我就建議大家如果仲留有既千奇唔好退群! ! !"},{"pid":"f14efb59f6203d2646e52be2f8e767af24284376","tid":2179181,"uid":229353,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:37:32.000Z","msg":"入都無入過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988fb414b10dc428b6fa6df4d31a91c15142e6ac","tid":2179181,"uid":9392,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:37:55.000Z","msg":"哂鳩氣啦 過兩年全部冇哂影啦"},{"pid":"7b9062d3c1753dc4680eba6baf16e6b6544636a7","tid":2179181,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:40:33.000Z","msg":"有開 但畢業完果個九月就冇再出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後果次係4年次約聚會 但係都係得平時會一個月見一次果班出席 晒氣"},{"pid":"1a4a7e1a2c91e6be26abc07a7610342a053d5d7a","tid":2179181,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:40:40.000Z","msg":"通常要精英全部人fg 50k<br />\n或者Band 3中學全部入唔到U<br />\n先會keep到<br />\n<br />\n高低落差較大就好難"},{"pid":"2d3fb4c2a0bcfd6bc2bae9b28b37f6b046dd601c","tid":2179181,"uid":57359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1a4a7e1a2c91e6be26abc07a7610342a053d5d7a","tid":2179181,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"reply